HEADWORD: Kalpa
<hw>Kal"pa</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.]</ety>
<fld>(Hind. Myth.)</fld> <def>One of the Brahmanic eons, a period of
4,320,000,000 years. At the end of each Kalpa the world is
annihilated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kalsomine</ent>⟦br⟧
